EncounterPostalCodeSearchParameter

Parameter address-postalcode:string

Searches based on the address-postalcode field for the Encounter record eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Encounter?address-postalcode={postalCode}

ResourceEncounter
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesEncounter
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
